從[ _Stepping Stones_](http://acrossthelana.blogspot.com/2009/02/vagabonds-in-
albania.html "http://acrossthelana.blogspot.com/2009/02/vagabonds-in-
albania.html")和[ _A Nevada Yankee in King Zogs
Court_](http://anevadayankeeinkingzogscourt.blogspot.com/
"http://anevadayankeeinkingzogscourt.blogspot.com/")發現的一個旅遊部落格，[ _Vagabond
Journey.com Travelogue_](http://www.vagabondjourney.com/travelogue
"http://www.vagabondjourney.com/travelogue")：9年遊遍五大洲裡至少40個國家。他最近的活動中心在阿爾巴尼亞（[這裡](http://www.vagabondjourney.com/travelogue/2009/02/mountains-
of-albania.html "http://www.vagabondjourney.com/travelogue/2009/02/mountains-
of-
albania.html")和[這裡](http://www.vagabondjourney.com/travelogue/2009/02/bunkers-
in-albania.html "http://www.vagabondjourney.com/travelogue/2009/02/bunkers-in-
albania.html")）。

校對：[Portnoy](http://taipedia.selfip.info/mediawiki/index.php/%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E8%80%85:Portnoy
"使用者:Portnoy")

